text: Rezgui is a surname, and may refer to; Rezgui derives from رزقي which means my living or my supper in Arabic. * Rakia Rezgui (born 1996) - Tunisian handball player * Wassim Rezgui (born 1986) - Tunisian football player *Seifeddine Rezgui - alleged perpretator of the 2015 Sousse attacks *Rezgui Guizani (1934-2015) - Tunisian boxer ==See also== *Monder Rizki ==References== Category:Arabic-language surnames Category:Surnames of Tunisian origin Category:Surnames of Algerian origin
title: Rezgui
